            "stanza_text": "Elles grincent, mes girouettes,\nSur le pauvre toit en lambeaux.\nTous les arbres, grands et nabots,\nOnt de lugubres silhouettes !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Dans la saison des alouettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Quand les cieux dorment sans flambeaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Elles grincent mes girouettes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Sur le pauvre toit en lambeaux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Dans la saison des alouettes,\nQuand les cieux dorment sans flambeaux,\nElles grincent mes girouettes\nSur le pauvre toit en lambeaux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Comme elles font des pirouettes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Dès que les jours ne sont plus beaux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Le matin, avec les corbeaux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Et le soir, avec les chouettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Elles grincent mes girouettes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Comme elles font des pirouettes\nDès que les jours ne sont plus beaux !\nLe matin, avec les corbeaux,\nEt le soir, avec les chouettes,\nElles grincent mes girouettes !"
